<P>A SHORT SKETCH OF THE EVIDENCE FOR THE ABOLITION OF THE SLAVE TRADE, <HI>Delivered before a Committee of the Hou&s;e of Commons.</HI> TO WHICH IS ADDED, A Recommendation of the Subject TO THE SERIOUS ATTENTION OF PEOPLE IN GENERAL.</P>
<Q><P>"ALL THINGS WHATSOEVER YE WOULD THAT MEN SHOULD DO TO YOU, DO YE EVEN SO TO THEM."</P>
<BIBL>Matt. chap. vii. ver. 12.</BIBL></Q>
<P>LONDON, PRINTED, PHILADELPHIA: RE-PRINTED BY DANIEL LAWRENCE. M.DCC.XCII.</P>
