<P>The De&s;ign of the following <HI>SHORT SKETCH</HI> is not to &s;uper&s;ede, in any Degree, <HI>MORE IMPORTANT PUB|LICATIONS,</HI> but, on the Contrary, to extend their Circulation, and promote their Influence.</P>
